<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/engineering-construction-industry-training-board> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Engineering Construction Industry Training Board (ECITB) ensures there are enough trained people to meet industry needs. It gives professional advice and offers skills development and qualifications to help individuals in the sector succeed in their chosen careers. ECITB is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Work and Pensions ."@en .
